GUILD: Guild membership commands

Syntax: guild info
        guild join <guild>
        guild leave
        guild list

DESCRIPTION:
  Manages your guild membership. Guilds provide bonuses and access to
  guild-specific skills, equipment, and areas.

  guild info       : shows your current guild and standing
  guild join <name>: applies to join a guild
  guild leave      : leaves your current guild
  guild list       : lists all available guilds

SEE ALSO: skills, faction
